thread.title: Lukasz Bartczak appointed IDH's temporary chairman of management
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Lukasz Bartczak appointed IDH's temporary chairman of management | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Lukasz Bartczak appointed IDH's temporary chairman of management
text:
Sept 16 IDH SA
* Its supervisory board delegated Lukasz Bartczak to perform duties of company's chairman of management board for three months as of Sept. 16
* Lukasz Bartczak is member of IDH's supervisory board Source text for Eikon: (Gdynia Newsroom)
